{"tid":348371,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"「非針對肥婆」大家返工有無咩肥婆特別黑人憎？","createTime":"2017-08-05T15:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T01:03:06.000Z","uid":118983,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e238000791a180f374a14cff848d674d515764","tid":348371,"uid":118983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T15:47:01.000Z","msg":"講下個肥婆嘅外表先 <br />\n好撚肥 成個欣宜咁撚樣 同時又好矮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日化行個妝 著短裙露臍裝 見到都想嘔 佢行過嘅時候千奇咪同佢有眼神接觸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係佢會問你：「做咩呀？覺得我好靚呀？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日日返到公司就例牌坐10-15分鐘先開始搵野做<br />\n每隔5分鐘就入一入office hea 大佬你hea唔緊要 你又要周圍r人吹水 又要用把高八度嘅死人聲係到嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地office入面平時會有野比大家食 當佢一見到補左啲野食 例牌每樣都拆開黎食 好食又貴果啲佢會食撚晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如豬古力之類<br />\n<br />\n講下佢食量 lunch 例如 食一個m記餐 一杯雪糕 返工司途中再加一杯野飲 一隻炸雞 魚蛋 燒賣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時仲唔夠食 叫人買返黎比佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係話有錢唔比你食 你食咁撚多係浪費資源<br />\n<br />\n收工前30分鐘例牌入左office坐 <br />\n<br />\n唔係話針對肥婆 但公司果個就咁岩係肥婆"},{"pid":"81727920c87225839e7a9953b4bb8f437fd144e9","tid":348371,"uid":118983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"純粹抒發下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肥婆真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"ecdf0b006c0a1cc843c1dd72c40c1b26156b3708","tid":348371,"uid":118983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T15:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家都無？"},{"pid":"fc31b620b6575e98145c8b8a1844e37a4734ac77","tid":348371,"uid":37760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"936eec271052589086848182